  "message": "\ud83d\udcdd readme: drop &v=4 cache-bust from ACMM badge URL\n\nThe cache-bust was only needed once when the badge function was newly\ndeployed and shields.io had cached an 'inaccessible' response for this\nspecific URL. With cacheSeconds:3600 (PR #8362) shields.io will refresh\non its own, so the magic param is now inert and just clutters the URL.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
